(11132, 'Tabocine 100mg 10 caps.', 'تابوسين 100 مجم 10 كبسولات', '31.5', '46', 'Doxycycline', 'Tabuk pharmaceutical manufacturing company', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مضاد حيوي', 'Antibiotic.tetracycline', '100mg', 'Doxycycline is indicated for the treatment of various infections by gram-positive and gram-negative bacteria, aerobes and anaerobes, as well other types of bacteria, including:
